Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: openq4-game
Architecture: any
Depends: openq4, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Quake 4 game modules for the openQ4 engine
 openQ4-GameLibs provides the single-player and multiplayer game library
 modules derived from the Quake 4 SDK, maintained for use with the
 openQ4 open-source engine replacement.
 .
 This package installs game-sp and game-mp shared modules into the
 openQ4 engine directory.
 .
